::Annihilator/Killer::

Annihalator grunts as he is thrown out of his chair and into a wall.

Killer stays in his chair. "Something is hitting the ship!" He types a few 
buttons and a visual turns on, showing shapes hitting the ship before it 
dissolves into static.

"We're being hit by astroids!" He yells, "The ship can't stay in orbit much 
longer!"
